title: Ore no Gikei ga UFO Yobou to Shiteru n desu kedo
original_name: 俺の義兄が UFO 呼ぼうとしてるんですけど
sinopse: Kazuho is a hardcore UFO otaku, much to the chagrin of his stepbrother Haruichi. But after getting roped into Kazuho's antics, Haruichi feels jealous when the UFO Research Club start getting involved too!
